high_descs: Turn around and walk to the right side of the television stand on the left.
Pick up the remote control from the right side of the stand.
Turn right, hang a right at the wall and walk to the tall lamp in the corner to the right.
Turn on the tall lamp in the corner.
anns.task_desc: Examine a remote control by the light of a tall lamp.

high_descs: Turn around and walk forward then toward the dresser with the TV on it.
Pick up the remote control on the right side of the dresser top, in front of the TV.
Turn around and walk to the lamp, on the other side of the room, to the standing lamp in the corner.
Put the remote control under the lampshade and turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Put a remote control under a lampshade to turn on the lamp.

high_descs: Turn around, go forward, then turn left to face the dresser with the TV on it.
Pick up the remote from the dresser.
Go forward for the bureau, then turn right to go to the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Look at the remote in the light of a lamp.
